		<section class="home-block">
			<div class="row">
				<div class="large-8 large-offset-2 home-block-header">
					<h1>Operations</h1>
					<p>How we meet our mandate.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
			
			
			
			
			  <div class="large-3 columns operation">
			    <a href="http://hqca.ca/health-care-provider-resources/"><img src="/assets/52700bd29cd7455cfe000010/initiatives_glyph.png" alt="Healthcare Provider Resources"></a>
			    <h3>Healthcare Provider Resources</h3>
			    <p>The HQCA produces publications and materials to help health professionals work toward improvement in areas of health service quality and patient safety. </p>
			    <a href="http://hqca.ca/health-care-provider-resources/">LEARN MORE</a>
			  </div>
		  
			
			
			  <div class="large-3 columns operation">
			    <a href="http://hqca.ca/studies-and-reviews/"><img src="/assets/52700e3d3cdb7c69b300007c/studies_reviews_glyph.png" alt="Studies and Reviews"></a>
			    <h3>Studies and Reviews</h3>
			    <p>The HQCA conducts studies and reviews of various facets of Alberta's healthcare system as part of our mandate to assess or study matters respecting patient safety and health service quality. </p>
			    <a href="http://hqca.ca/studies-and-reviews/">LEARN MORE</a>
			  </div>
		  
			
			
			  <div class="large-3 columns operation">
			    <a href="http://hqca.ca/surveys/"><img src="/assets/52700e85c0d7cd2db70000a3/measurement_glyph.png" alt="Surveys"></a>
			    <h3>Surveys</h3>
			    <p>Surveys provide the HQCA with vital insight into Albertans' experiences with the healthcare system and are a key measure of quality and source of information to improve care and services.</p>
			    <a href="http://hqca.ca/surveys/">LEARN MORE</a>
			  </div>
		  
			
			
			  <div class="large-3 columns operation">
			    <a href="http://hqca.ca/education/"><img src="/assets/52700ec2c0d7cd0ad3000269/education_glyph.png" alt="Education"></a>
			    <h3>Education</h3>
			    <p>The HQCA, often in partnership with our stakeholders, offers educational opportunities and practical tools to benefit individuals and teams who are dedicated to improving patient safety and quality. </p>
			    <a href="http://hqca.ca/education/">LEARN MORE</a>
			  </div>
		  
			
			
			
			</div>
		</section>
